text: Haji Muhammad Ismael Seela (; is a Pakistani Politician, currently serving as Member of the Provincial Assembly of the Punjab from 23 February 2024. He preceded Rana Ahmad Shahryyar in 2024 Pakistani General Elections. == Political career == He was elected to the Provincial Assembly of the Punjab as a candidate of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf from Constituency PP-116 Faisalabad XIX. He defeated Ahmad Shehryar, a candidate of Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N), receiving 67,016 votes to 52,496 votes. == References == Category:Politicians from Punjab, Pakistan
title: Muhammad Ismael
